N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 164.10 - Monitoring

State Regulations

Employees and agents of the division responsible for
monitoring, inspecting, supervising, and investigating programs operated by the
division shall have access to confidential HIV information to the extent
necessary to discharge those responsibilities. Notes
